author: Laurence Small
title: Laurence Small
text: wanted new exhaust was undecided what to buy so opted for mtc twin outlet pipe . spoke too martin on friday system arrived on tuesday morning all parts are very well made and easy to assemble . job completed in approx an hour started up and now my blade sounds so so sweet and crispy ! will be recomending to my friends with out a doubt ! 10 out o 10 start to finish !!
